##Custom Templates
The default template anatomy: 

    \{{index}}
    \{{modules}}
    \{{globals}}
    \{{others}}
    
###Index
Only output if there are at least two modules defined. 

    #Index
    
    * Modules
      * \{{module-name}}
        * \{{module-members}}
    * Global
      * \{{global-members}}

